Reset your password
===================

We received a request to reset the password for <%= @user.email_address %>.

Click the link below to choose a new password (expires in 15 minutes):

<%= "#{ENV.fetch('FRONTEND_URL', 'http://localhost:3000')}/reset-password?token=#{@user.generate_token_for(:password_reset)}" %>

If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
